Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Rio Hondo in Zamboanga City to Kauman Muslimin
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 680
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Rio Hondo in Zamboanga City to Kauman Muslimin
Section 1. The name of Barangay Rio Hondo in Zamboanga City is hereby changed to Kauman Muslimin.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
